        - <span>BRIEFING</span>
        - <span role="byline"></span>
    </section>

    <p>With the growth of e-com­merce amid the pandemic, SingPost is look­ing to re­vamp its postal in­fra­struc­ture. To kick-start this ef­fort, it will be con­duct­ing a pub­lic trial of its smart let­ter­box sys­tem in the com­ing months. In­stead of in­di­vid­ual let­ter­boxes, this sys­tem en­tails a cen­tral ma­chine that stores and dis­penses mail and small pack­ages.</p>


